title: Deilie Jock
author: Campbell, C. M.
snippet: Sae I marched doon Regent Street, and WaterlooPlace, and Cockspur Street, past the HorseGuards to Westminster, and back to WellingtonBarracks, by Bird Cage Walk—the very oppositedirection to what I would ha' come if I had gonestraicht back from Bobe's beat.
